A small addition on top of the ServerPerks' Scoreboard to show:

- Headshots
- Husks
- Scrakes
- Fleshpounds

kills per player

[H1][b][u]Notes[/u][/b][/H1]

For Players:

- This has only been tested on ServerPerks
- This REQUIRES ServerPerks

For Devs:

- This might work on your ScoreBoards if they are extending SP ScoreBoard

[H1][b][u]Number Of Files[/u][/b][/H1]

- 2

[H1][b][u]File Names[/u][/b][/H1]

- \System\KFEnhancedScoreboard.u
- \System\KFEnhancedScoreboard.ucl

[H1][b][u]Usage[/u][/b][/H1]

1- Subscribe or download manually (recommended)
2- Launch the game and wait to see 'Completed'
3- Restart the game and you can see the mutators in your list

[H1][b][u]Class Names[/u][/b][/H1]

- KFEnhancedScoreboard.KFEnhancedScoreboard

